title: Independent candidate Usman Ali wins NA-142 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent Usman Ali has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-142 Sahiwal-II by securing 1,07,496 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz candidate Ch Muhammad Ashraf, who bagged 96,125 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 53.74 percent.
